    • Uses of Role in org.jamwiki.model

      Fields in org.jamwiki.model declared as Role 
      Modifier and Type Field and Description
      static Role Role.ROLE_ADMIN
      ROLE_ADMIN gives permission to perform wiki maintenance tasks not available to normal users.
      static Role Role.ROLE_ANONYMOUS
      ROLE_ANONYMOUS is not stored in the database but is instead automatically assigned to all non-logged in users by Spring Security.
      static Role Role.ROLE_EDIT_EXISTING 
      static Role Role.ROLE_EDIT_NEW 
      static Role Role.ROLE_EMBEDDED
      ROLE_EMBEDDED is meant for use with installations that perform authentication and user management in an external system, such as LDAP.
      static Role Role.ROLE_IMPORT
      Role used to control who can import new topics to the wiki using Special:Import.
      static Role Role.ROLE_MOVE 
      static Role Role.ROLE_NO_ACCOUNT
      ROLE_NO_ACCOUNT is meant for use with installations that do not allow user account management from within JAMWiki.
      static Role Role.ROLE_REGISTER
      Allow users to self-register.
      static Role Role.ROLE_SYSADMIN
